\subsubsection{3.6.1 HPO Annotations
Corpus}\label{hpo-annotations-corpus}

We constructed our evaluation dataset from the HPO phenotype annotation
file (phenotype.hpoa), which contains curated disease-phenotype
associations from multiple authoritative sources (Köhler et al., 2021).

\textbf{Table 1: HPO Annotations Dataset Summary}

