\subsubsection{F.3 Privacy-Utility Tradeoff
Curve}\label{f.3-privacy-utility-tradeoff-curve}

\begin{verbatim}
nDCG@10
  │
1.0├───●────●────●                    ● Baseline (no privacy)
   │        ╲                         ● ε = 10
0.9├──────────●──────●                ● ε = 5
   │              ╲                   ● ε = 2
0.8├───────────────────●              ● ε = 1
   │                     ╲
0.7├────────────────────────●         ● ε = 0.5
   │
0.6├─────────────────────────────●    ● ε = 0.1
   │
   └──┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬─────▶ Privacy (1/ε)
     0.1    0.2    0.5    1.0    2.0

Recommended Operating Range: ε ∈ [2.0, 5.0]
   - High utility (>93% nDCG@10)
   - Meaningful privacy guarantees
\end{verbatim}

